3. install from tar.gz with pip
----------------------------------
* electrum = bitcoin wallet
  1. sudo apt-get install python-qt4 python-pip
  2. sudo pip2 install https://download.electrum.org/2.9.3/Electrum-2.9.3.tar.gz


4. add repository and then install
-----------------------------------
* atom = text editor
  1. sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/atom
  2. sudo apt update; sudo apt install atom


5. mate desktop
-----------------------

